data.description: Step into this impeccably maintained residence bathed in natural light, crafting a welcoming and cozy ambiance. Nestled in a sought-after location in close proximity to USAA, the Medical Center, UTSA, La Cantera, and the Rim, this four-bedroom dwelling, complemented by an extra office space, situates you in the heart of the vibrant NW side. Boasting generously sized rooms, encompassing four bedrooms and a bonus office area, this home offers abundant space for both relaxed living and efficient work. Nestled on a corner lot at the entrance of a cul-de-sac, a sense of tranquility embraces you. Nearby walking trails beckon, providing an ideal escape into nature just a few steps away. The backyard transforms into a private sanctuary adorned with flourishing fruit trees, a covered patio, and the perfect inclusion of stainless steel appliances, including a double oven-an optimal arrangement for hosting lively BBQs with friends or savoring the outdoors in serenity.
